Interface IHasMonolingualExternalRefs

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Context, HasMonolingualExternalRefs, SemanticLabel, Sense, Synset

    public interface IHasMonolingualExternalRefs
    Interface for UBY-LMF classes containing one or more references to an external system, represented by MonolingualExternalRef instances.
    Author:
    Zijad Maksuti

    • Method Detail

      • getMonolingualExternalRefs

        java.util.List<MonolingualExternalRef> getMonolingualExternalRefs()
        Returns the List of all MonolingualExternalRef instances which link this UBY-LMF class instance to an external system.
        Returns:
        the list of all monolingual external references of this UBY-LMF class instance or an empty list if the instance does not have any monolingual external references set

        monolingualExternalRefs - the monolingual external references to set
